				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't have highsun yet, but i've still been working on my epic during times I can't find any groups.
<br />

<br />
You can find the eldrig ph entirely solo without highun also and it's not too difficult really. The ph seems to roam back and forth nearby BW zone in after it has been up a while. So what you can do is run there, and start killing roamers in the area. I just charmed them on each other and dotted up for fast killing. Set a timer for 11 mins immediately when the first one dies. Keep killing until time is up and then run back to the loc N560 N4014. Respawn is 13 mins so you will have time before it pops. Then just stick around at the spawn point for another 13 mins to see if it pops there from the mobs you killed.
<br />

<br />
I had to do this twice (took a bit under 1 hour total) to get the ph, but now i'm camping its spawn point and killing it each time it pops. Knowing you are killing the right mob helps a lot with the patience of this camp. Right now i'm on PH #18 after around 5 hours here. My luck never has been good, but I know it will spawn, eventually. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /></span></td>
